%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6
%% Source: architecture/rhoai-3.4-ea.1/trustyai-service-operator.md

sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / Client
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant TASCtrl as TAS Controller
    participant Route as OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS reencrypt
    participant KRBP as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant TASvc as TrustyAI Service<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant LMESCtrl as LMES Controller
    participant LMPod as LM Eval Pod<br/>+ Driver Sidecar
    participant Model as Model Endpoint<br/>HTTP/HTTPS
    participant GORCHCtrl as GORCH Controller
    participant Orch as Orchestrator<br/>8032/TCP HTTP
    participant KServe as KServe InferenceService

    Note over User, TASvc: Flow 1: TrustyAI Service Deployment & Access
    User->>K8sAPI: Create TrustyAIService CR<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    K8sAPI-->>TASCtrl: Watch event
    TASCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create Deployment, Service,<br/>Route, PVC, ServiceMonitor
    TASCtrl->>K8sAPI: Patch InferenceService<br/>payloadProcessor
    User->>Route: HTTPS request<br/>TLS reencrypt
    Route->>KRBP: Forward (8443/TCP)<br/>TLS
    KRBP->>K8sAPI: SubjectAccessReview<br/>Auth validation
    K8sAPI-->>KRBP: Authorized
    KRBP->>TASvc: Forward (8080/TCP)<br/>HTTP plaintext (localhost)
    TASvc-->>KRBP: Response
    KRBP-->>Route: Response (HTTPS)
    Route-->>User: Response (HTTPS)

    Note over User, Model: Flow 2: LM Evaluation Job Execution
    User->>K8sAPI: Create LMEvalJob CR<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    K8sAPI-->>LMESCtrl: Watch event
    LMESCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create Pod with driver sidecar
    LMPod->>Model: Evaluation requests<br/>HTTP/HTTPS varies
    Model-->>LMPod: Model responses
    LMPod->>K8sAPI: Update LMEvalJob status<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token

    Note over User, KServe: Flow 3: Guardrails Orchestrator
    User->>K8sAPI: Create GuardrailsOrchestrator CR<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    K8sAPI-->>GORCHCtrl: Watch event
    GORCHCtrl->>K8sAPI: List KServe InferenceServices
    GORCHCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create ConfigMaps, Deployment,<br/>Service, Routes
    User->>Route: Client request (HTTPS)
    Route->>Orch: Forward to orchestrator
    Orch->>KServe: Generation request<br/>HTTP/HTTPS + TLS
    KServe-->>Orch: Generation response
    Orch-->>Route: Orchestrated response
    Route-->>User: Response (HTTPS)
